https://github.com/nikhilroxtomar/Chatroom-in-C

Discussed with:
Jason sebastian on how to check status and socket connection
Felic lionardo on how to cancel threads and memmory loss

To Run use the command below:
1. make
2. ./lets-talk 6000 localhost 6001 
	on the first terminal
3. ./lets-talk 6000 localhost 6001
	in the second terminal on the same folder

start typing use double enter to send the message, this is done so that the message can include multiple lines even paragraphs. Use !status to check if the destination terminal is connected.

